com.samskivert.depot

Class Stats.Snapshot

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.samskivert.depot.Stats.Snapshot
  • Enclosing class:
    Stats

    public static class Stats.Snapshot
extends Object
    An immutable class used to report statistics on repository activity. Statistics are tracked from the start of the VM and are never reset.
